master.title: Use this channel to post ads for your group content!
master.description:
You must be in a voice channel!
Post your ads in the format:
 `.invite [among_us|skribbl] [invite]`

broadcast.title: This is a broadcast channel for the BigRed Bot!
broadcast.description:
Invite posts that are made on the CU server will be copied here.
Clicking on the link in the descriptions will let you join the group in a voice party!
Head over to CU to make your own LFG posts!
